{"tid":269114,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(歐洲三國行山直播)170公里環白朗峰步道Tour du Mont Blanc","createTime":"2017-06-03T14:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T02:51:52.000Z","uid":110155,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e479cb8de27d6b2dab42d378ce7ac2a803680b8a","tid":269114,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:02:01.000Z","msg":"Tour du Mont Blanc，意爲環歐洲阿爾卑斯山脈最高峰白朗峰(Mont Blanc，海拔4807m）的徒步路線，是歐洲知名度最高，也是最受歡迎的徒步路線之一，被美國國家地理評爲世界二十條最好的徒步路線之一。TMB全程圍繞勃朗峰前進，橫跨瑞士、意大利、法國三國邊境，徒步路線總長約170公里，對於大多數徒步者來說總共需要時間爲8至11天，平均每天徒步15公里。<br />\n<br />\n我預計唔會行得大快，估計8日左右，因為行完之後會飛去冰島行另一條路線，而個條路線會係大約6月15日開，所以行得太快都無用。<br />\n<br />\n宜家我去緊機場，準備飛去蘇黎世，再轉機去日內瓦，再坐巴士去沙木尼(chamonix)，開始行TMB。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lfk98ita\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flfk98ita&h=0dda46df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/37fcim2a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F37fcim2a&h=4c6387ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為左慳啲錢，係香港帶5日食物過去，未計水，約16公斤，前面再加個Day pack同相機3公斤"},{"pid":"3452cb69fec31303f4555f3a58dde67525a6b915","tid":269114,"uid":69417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b080a12304607637445b1e440fb1423e16ce0d1","tid":269114,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/l1w26qby\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fl1w26qby&h=843b9024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/g1oyqmvi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fg1oyqmvi&h=f434c678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kzwrhtj9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkzwrhtj9&h=6a84abb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e789746d4f577e4b02d90fdfd9f6fa632ec8fd","tid":269114,"uid":11077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:41:15.000Z","msg":"諗住有mont blanc 睇<br />\n點知你仲係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b183c437aa9fbf568b3c8c55236238fe975bae7","tid":269114,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:42:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗住有mont blanc 睇<br />\n點知你仲係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慢慢黎啦，直播"},{"pid":"d862cc36e80313d592c9eccb6163b9ad9eb050d8","tid":269114,"uid":26302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:48:17.000Z","msg":"留名睇靚相"},{"pid":"5561861b5ab01cccbab59e4fb3b1503eff4bfb01","tid":269114,"uid":95237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:50:41.000Z","msg":"LM睇相 加油"},{"pid":"a217a4a2754ca4c1fe50ac3f810985540db530c0","tid":269114,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/a0oemi1b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa0oemi1b&h=de6af495&s={SIZE}\" />0005上機"},{"pid":"d19997537d458b256be9ec2956d6366cfa20dc64","tid":269114,"uid":1666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:13:09.000Z","msg":"正！劉明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2fee627cf8c5ebf14315ae1e600d746d465284","tid":269114,"uid":84163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:17:42.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1671329585906681d37952437feb379575bcbbe","tid":269114,"uid":11077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T02:56:58.000Z","msg":"到未呀"},{"pid":"2593c05253247d6244d36e9603c0657cb7fb24b3","tid":269114,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:12:11.000Z","msg":"到左蘇黎世，因為未買轉機機票，所以決定坐火車去日內瓦，好似好玩啲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lau0fz2i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flau0fz2i&h=70e4b8b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pbi4gej2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpbi4gej2&h=b1195d74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白痴嘅係，之前買張N國可用電話卡，居然瑞士。。。宜家用機場wifi上網，要去到法國先用到。。。"},{"pid":"a21560c3f272a32bc6517ff9ec0e1013225c3f15","tid":269114,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:18:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到左蘇黎世，因為未買轉機機票，所以決定坐火車去日內瓦，好似好玩啲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lau0fz2i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flau0fz2i&h=70e4b8b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pbi4gej2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpbi4gej2&h=b1195d74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白痴嘅係，之前買張N國可用電話卡，居然瑞士。。。宜家用機場wifi上網，要去到法國先用到。。。</blockquote><br />\n無瑞士"},{"pid":"e11343c701b73532421d99cd086d8058829124be","tid":269114,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:14:09.000Z","msg":"為左慳少少錢，決定唔坐飛機火車去日內瓦，而係用個app揾共乘，飛機大約係100歐，火車要70，共乘只係20歐！<br />\n<br />\n之後好順利咁去到日內瓦機場，再次揾揾揾車，宜家去緊沙木尼！"},{"pid":"59e7d29480ee0610a228503e855965cf35152730","tid":269114,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:03:01.000Z","msg":"來到第一站蘇黎世，很快我就發現自己出現第一個問題，我買的N國上網電話卡，有法國有意大利有冰島，就是沒有瑞士，所以剛下機就沒辦法上網了。<br />\n<br />\n對於我來說，不能上網不會阻礙我的行程，但是我遇到每一個狀況，令我非常狼狽。<br />\n<br />\n我本來打算到達蘇黎世後，再買轉機到日內瓦的機票，但因為機票比預想中貴，所以就看看有沒有更便宜的交通。結果，經朋友介紹，找到了提供共乘資訊的平台，又讓我找到時間剛好的司機，價錢大約只是飛機的五分之一，而且可以和其他人聊天，這樣會更加有趣。<br />\n<br />\n問題是，我需要網絡才能確保我找到要坐的那輛車，所以我只能先告訴司機我的衣著和紅色大背包，再拿到他的車牌號碼，希望他會準時出現，不會有什麼意外。<br />\n<br />\n結果，真的沒什麼意外，司機順利找到我，再加兩個旅客，就出發到日內瓦。到了日內瓦後，我再找到前往沙木尼的巴士，正式向目的地進發！<br />\n<br />\n當我來到沙木尼，買了一個登山指南後，才發現原來TMB根本沒有通過沙木尼，而是在附近的小鎮Les Houches，當我打算走大約一小時過去時，有一輛車主動停下，問我要不要坐順風車！<br />\n<br />\nBenja先開車帶我來到Les Houches，才發現這裡的店全關了，加上明天也是假期，我不可能在這裡買到煮食用的氣罐，所以他又把我載回沙木尼買氣罐，再告訴我今天可以在哪露營。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我今天並不會正常出發，而是明天再坐巴士(Benja說巴士是免費，根本不用走過去)到Les Houches，再正式起步！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r47g81z3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr47g81z3&h=a6985f23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zuq9iaxg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzuq9iaxg&h=378468e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/25ct6r1w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F25ct6r1w&h=a03eaeed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8163a429b38715686d1d73e5507fb7c4ebd9d6d1","tid":269114,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:03:56.000Z","msg":"晚餐now<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/drb3no6g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdrb3no6g&h=353b47fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98e63cbd395f793de53d3ee333bf5a1d921ec0b8","tid":269114,"uid":11077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:51:38.000Z","msg":"咁好人 車你入去又車返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3774d625c303a12437b60e0102600e51bc2b6313","tid":269114,"uid":11077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:52:31.000Z","msg":"出發未呀"},{"pid":"d44da4266a3e37a0ef4e7d4653eace83e9bf1f41","tid":269114,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:19:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b48febc48606e83c116af4319370c3e99f5f44c9","tid":269114,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出發未呀</blockquote><br />\n行緊第二日，因為網絡太差，直播唔到。。。遲啲開po一次過更新"},{"pid":"f23650a2edf0e023ad8a4c091a3f6276b18044f3","tid":269114,"uid":265932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b48febc48606e83c116af4319370c3e99f5f44c9","tid":269114,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出發未呀</blockquote><br />\n行緊第二日，因為網絡太差，直播唔到。。。遲啲開po一次過更新"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:51:52.000Z","msg":"想問咁多日徒步洗咗幾錢"}]}